data.description: Welcome Home!  You will love this home in the sought after Southern Plantation neighborhood.  Barbers Hill ISD. Great Home With Over 1/2 Acre Lot, And A Pool!!! This 4/5 bedroom home has room for all the family, a large yard and pool for the kids/family and the fur baby's to run & play in.  There are 2 extra rooms upstairs that can be used for an office, game room, flex room... House has no carpet!  Pool is fabulous and the pool deck has been resurfaced within the last year. Pool controls are digital and can be controlled from your phone. Bose surround sound in patio area.  There is a pool house as well with portable AC/Heat unit.  There is a play ground in the back of the neighborhood and a boat ramp!!!  Home is located in BHISD school district.  Close proximity to I-10, Toll Rd 99, and FM 1409.  Close to HEB, lots of retail, restaurants, Medical facilities, plus low taxes!  This could be your home so make your appointment today.
